data.description: This charming 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom home with a basement comes with such a cozy feeling. The large driveway provides ample parking for multiple vehicles, and the fenced backyard offers a great space for cookouts and entertainment.  Located in a great location, this home is close to schools, shops, and parks, making it ideal for those looking for convenience and accessibility. The interior features a spacious living area a well-equipped kitchen, and two comfortable bedrooms. The basement can be used as a rec room, home office, or additional storage space. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this desirable and cozy home in a great location. Contact us today for more information or to schedule a viewing!
